# AI Guidelines

## Behavior
- Direct and concise - no apologies/confirmations
- Focus on solutions over explanations
- Don't ask for verification of visible info
- Real file links, not placeholders

## Workflow  
- File-by-file changes when requested
- Complete edits in one response per file
- Preserve existing code
- Use TodoWrite for multi-step tasks

## Code quality
- Verify before presenting
- Use search tools extensively
- Follow project patterns
- No unnecessary comments